HEADWORD: Lightning
<hw>Light"ning</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧t"n⟦icr⟧ng)</pr>, <pos>vb. n.</pos>
<def>Lightening.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Light-o'-love</ent>⟦br⟧
